o Cloud Code! Please wait while we prepare dependencies on your machine.\nCloud Code maintains and uses a suite of best-in-class Cloud Native devtools on your machine including [Cloud SDK](https://cloud.google.com/sdk), [Kubectl](https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/kubectl/), [Minikube](https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/), and [Skaffold](https://skaffold.dev/)."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.kubectlExplorer","when":"gcloudComponentsInstalling","contents":"Welcome to Cloud Code! Please wait while we prepare dependencies on your machine.\nCloud Code maintains and uses a suite of best-in-class Cloud Native devtools on your machine including [Cloud SDK](https://cloud.google.com/sdk), [Kubectl](https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/kubectl/), [Minikube](https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/), and [Skaffold](https://skaffold.dev/)."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.kubernetes.localDevExplorer","when":"gcloudComponentsInstalling","contents":"Welcome to Cloud Code! Please wait while we prepare dependencies on your machine.\nCloud Code maintains and uses a suite of best-in-class Cloud Native devtools on your machine including [Cloud SDK](https://cloud.google.com/sdk), [Kubectl](https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/kubectl/), [Minikube](https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/), and [Skaffold](https://skaffold.dev/)."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.cloudRunExplorer","when":"!gcloudInstalling && !authLoggedIn","contents":"Please login to Google Cloud to continue. If you don't have an account yet, you can get started with a [free trial](https://cloud.google.com/free).\n[Login to Google Cloud](command:cloudcode.gke.runGcloudAuth)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.secretsExplorer","when":"!gcloudInstalling && !authLoggedIn","contents":"Please login to Google Cloud to continue. If you don't have an account yet, you can get started with a [free trial](https://cloud.google.com/free).\n[Login to Google Cloud](command:cloudcode.gke.runGcloudAuth)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.gceExplorer","when":"!gcloudInstalling && !authLoggedIn","contents":"Please login to Google Cloud to continue. If you don't have an account yet, you can get started with a [free trial](https://cloud.google.com/free).\n[Login to Google Cloud](command:cloudcode.gke.runGcloudAuth)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.dataprocExplorer","when":"!gcloudInstalling && !authLoggedIn","contents":"Please login to Google Cloud to continue. If you don't have an account yet, you can get started with a [free trial](https://cloud.google.com/free).\n[Login to Google Cloud](command:cloudcode.gke.runGcloudAuth)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.bigQueryDatasetExplorer","when":"!gcloudInstalling && !authLoggedIn","contents":"Please login to Google Cloud to continue. If you don't have an account yet, you can get started with a [free trial](https://cloud.google.com/free).\n[Login to Google Cloud](command:cloudcode.gke.runGcloudAuth)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.gcsExplorer","when":"!gcloudInstalling && !authLoggedIn","contents":"Please login to Google Cloud to continue. If you don't have an account yet, you can get started with a [free trial](https://cloud.google.com/free).\n[Login to Google Cloud](command:cloudcode.gke.runGcloudAuth)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.cloudRunExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && !authProjectId","contents":"Please select a Google Cloud project continue. If you don't have a project yet, you can create one in [Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com/projectcreate).\n[Select a project](command:cloudcode.sharedExplorer.chooseProject)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.secretsExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && !authProjectId","contents":"Please select a Google Cloud project continue. If you don't have a project yet, you can create one in [Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com/projectcreate).\n[Select a project](command:cloudcode.sharedExplorer.chooseProject)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.gceExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && !authProjectId","contents":"Please select a Google Cloud project continue. If you don't have a project yet, you can create one in [Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com/projectcreate).\n[Select a project](command:cloudcode.sharedExplorer.chooseProject)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.cloudRunExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && !authProjectId && !runningOnCloudShell","contents":"If you want to select a project in another account, you can [sign out](command:cloudcode.gke.gcloudSignout) and sign back in."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.secretsExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && !authProjectId && !runningOnCloudShell","contents":"If you want to select a project in another account, you can [sign out](command:cloudcode.gke.gcloudSignout) and sign back in."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.gceExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && !authProjectId && !runningOnCloudShell","contents":"If you want to select a project in another account, you can [sign out](command:cloudcode.gke.gcloudSignout) and sign back in."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.dataprocExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && authProjectId && dataprocExplorerNeedsApiEnable","contents":"In order to use Cloud Dataproc on Google Cloud, you need to enable the [Cloud Dataproc API](https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/dataproc.googleapis.com).\nConsuming Google Cloud APIs may incur additional billing charges. You can learn more by clicking the above link.\n[Enable Cloud Dataproc API](command:cloudcode.dataprocExplorer.enableApi)\nAlternatively, you can [switch projects](command:cloudcode.sharedExplorer.chooseProject) to a project that already has this API enabled."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.bigQueryDatasetExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && authProjectId && dataplexExplorerNeedsApiEnable","contents":"In order to use Cloud Dataplex on Google Cloud, you need to enable the [Cloud Dataplex API](https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/dataplex.googleapis.com).\nConsuming Google Cloud APIs may incur additional billing charges. You can learn more by clicking the above link.\n[Enable Cloud Dataplex API](command:cloudcode.dataplexExplorer.enableApi)\nAlternatively, you can [switch projects](command:cloudcode.sharedExplorer.chooseProject) to a project that already has this API enabled."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.cloudRunExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && authProjectId && runExplorerNeedsApiEnable","contents":"In order to use Cloud Run on Google Cloud, you need to enable the [Cloud Run API](https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/run.googleapis.com).\nConsuming Google Cloud APIs may incur additional billing charges. You can learn more by clicking the above link.\n[Enable Cloud Run API](command:cloudcode.runExplorer.enableApi)\nAlternatively, you can [switch projects](command:cloudcode.sharedExplorer.chooseProject) to a project that already has this API enabled."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.secretsExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && authProjectId && secretmanagerExplorerNeedsApiEnable","contents":"In order to use Secret Manager on Google Cloud, you need to enable the [Secret Manager API](https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/secretmanager.googleapis.com).\nConsuming Google Cloud APIs may incur additional billing charges. You can learn more by clicking the above link.\n[Enable Secret Manager API](command:cloudcode.secretmanagerExplorer.enableApi)\nAlternatively, you can [switch projects](command:cloudcode.sharedExplorer.chooseProject) to a project that already has this API enabled."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.gceExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && authProjectId && computeExplorerNeedsApiEnable","contents":"In order to use Compute Engine on Google Cloud, you need to enable the [Compute API](https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/compute.googleapis.com).\nConsuming Google Cloud APIs may incur additional billing charges. You can learn more by clicking the above link.\n[Enable Compute API](command:cloudcode.computeExplorer.enableApi)\nAlternatively, you can [switch projects](command:cloudcode.sharedExplorer.chooseProject) to a project that already has this API enabled."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.gcfExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && authProjectId && cloudfunctionsExplorerNeedsApiEnable","contents":"In order to use Cloud Functions on Google Cloud, you need to enable the [Cloud Functions API](https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/cloudfunctions.googleapis.com) and [Cloud Build API](https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/cloudbuild.googleapis.com).\nConsuming Google Cloud APIs may incur additional billing charges. You can learn more by clicking the above link.\n[Enable Cloud Function and dependent APIs](command:cloudcode.functions.enableApi)\nAlternatively, you can [switch projects](command:cloudcode.sharedExplorer.chooseProject) to a project that already has these APIs enabled."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.cloudStorageExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && authProjectId && storageExplorerNeedsApiEnable","contents":"In order to use Cloud Storage on Google Cloud, you need to enable the [Cloud Storage API](https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/storage.googleapis.com).\nConsuming Google Cloud APIs may incur additional billing charges. You can learn more by clicking the above link.\n[Enable Cloud Storage API](command:cloudcode.cloudStorageExplorer.enableApi)\nAlternatively, you can [switch projects](command:cloudcode.sharedExplorer.chooseProject) to a project that already has this API enabled."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.gcfExplorer","when":"gcloudInstalling","contents":"Welcome to Cloud Code! Please wait while we prepare dependencies on your machine.\nCloud Code maintains and uses a suite of best-in-class Cloud Native devtools on your machine including [Cloud SDK](https://cloud.google.com/sdk), [Kubectl](https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/kubectl/), [Minikube](https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/), and [Skaffold](https://skaffold.dev/)."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.gcfExplorer","when":"!gcloudInstalling && !authLoggedIn","contents":"Please login to Google Cloud to continue. If you don't have an account yet, you can get started with a [free trial](https://cloud.google.com/free).\n[Login to Google Cloud](command:cloudcode.gke.runGcloudAuth)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.gcfExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && !authProjectId && !remoteCloudFunctionsAvailable && !validFunctionsWorkspace","contents":"You can select a project to work with Cloud Functions.\n[Select a project](command:cloudcode.sharedExplorer.chooseProject)\nYou can [create a function](command:cloudcode.functions.create) or [open a function workspace](command:cloudcode.functions.openWorkspace) locally.\nIf you have already opened a function, [set this workspace as a function workspace.](command:cloudcode.functions.annotateWorkspace)\n[Create function](command:cloudcode.functions.create)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.gcfExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && !authProjectId && !runningOnCloudShell","contents":"If you want to select a project in another account, you can [sign out](command:cloudcode.gke.gcloudSignout) and sign back in."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.gcfExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && authProjectId && !remoteCloudFunctionsAvailable && !validFunctionsWorkspace","contents":"We did not find any functions under the current project. [Select a different project](command:cloudcode.sharedExplorer.chooseProject)\nYou can [create a function](command:cloudcode.functions.create) or [open a function workspace](command:cloudcode.functions.openWorkspace) locally.\nIf you have already opened a function, [set this workspace as a function workspace.](command:cloudcode.functions.annotateWorkspace)\n[Create function](command:cloudcode.functions.create)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.notebookExplorer","when":"!gcloudInstalling && !authLoggedIn","contents":"Please login to Google Cloud to continue. If you don't have an account yet, you can get started with a [free trial](https://cloud.google.com/free).\n[Login to Google Cloud](command:cloudcode.gke.runGcloudAuth)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.cloudStorageExplorer","when":"gcloudInstalling","contents":"Welcome to Cloud Code! Please wait while we prepare dependencies on your machine.\nCloud Code maintains and uses a suite of best-in-class Cloud Native devtools on your machine including [Cloud SDK](https://cloud.google.com/sdk), [Kubectl](https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/kubectl/), [Minikube](https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/), and [Skaffold](https://skaffold.dev/)."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.cloudStorageExplorer","when":"!gcloudInstalling && !authLoggedIn","contents":"Please login to Google Cloud to continue. If you don't have an account yet, you can get started with a [free trial](https://cloud.google.com/free).\n[Login to Google Cloud](command:cloudcode.gke.runGcloudAuth)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.cloudStorageExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && !authProjectId","contents":"Please select a Google Cloud project continue. If you don't have a project yet, you can create one in [Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com/projectcreate).\n[Select a project](command:cloudcode.sharedExplorer.chooseProject)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.cloudStorageExplorer","when":"authLoggedIn && !authProjectId && !runningOnCloudShell","contents":"If you want to select a project in another account, you can [sign out](command:cloudcode.gke.gcloudSignout) and sign back in."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.kubectlExplorer","when":"!gcloudComponentsInstalling","contents":"Get started with Kubernetes in Cloud Code by adding a cluster to your KubeConfig. Clicking the button below is a good place to start, even if you don't have a cluster already.\n[Add a cluster to the KubeConfig](command:cloudcode.addClusterToConfig)\nAlternatively, if you already have a KubeConfig file, you can [load the file](command:cloudcode.switchKubeConfig)."},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.kubernetes.localDevExplorer","when":"!gcloudComponentsInstalling","contents":"Run or debug your kubernetes app using the options in the title bar or the options below.\n[Create a Kubernetes sample](command:cloudcode.createK8sAppExplorerTitle)\n[Run on Kubernetes](command:cloudcode.runK8sAppExplorerTitle)\n[Debug on Kubernetes](command:cloudcode.debugK8sAppExplorerTitle)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.mcdcSources","when":"isRunOnLinux && !m2cToolsInstalled","contents":"Replatform applications to containers on GKE.\n[Install tools](command:cloudcode.migrateToContainers.installTools)\n[Edit tools paths](command:cloudcode.migrateToContainers.editToolsPaths)"},{"view":"cloudcode.unified.mcdcSources","when":"isRunOnLinux && m2cToolsInstalled","contents":"Replatform applications to containers on GKE.\n[Edit Sources](command:cloudcode.migrateToContainers.mcdc.editSources)"}],"views":{"1-cloudCodeContainer":[{"id":"cloudcode.unified.kubernetes.localDevExplorer","name":"Development Sessions","icon":"images/kubernetes_logo.svg","visibility":"collapsed"},{"id":"cloudcode.unified.kubectlExplorer","name":"Kubernetes","icon":"images/kubernetes_logo.svg","visibility":"collapsed"},{"id":"cloudcode.unified.cloudRunExplorer","name":"Cloud Run","icon":"images/cloud_run_logo.svg","visibility":"collapsed"},{"id":"cloudcode.unified.apiExplorer","name":"Cloud APIs","icon":"images/cloud_api_logo.svg","visibility":"collapsed"},{"id":"cloudcode.unified.gcsExplorer","name":"Cloud Storage","icon":"images/google_cloud.svg","when":"config.cloudcode.beta.enableGcsExplorer","visibility":"collapsed"},{"id":"cloudcode.unified.dataprocExplorer","name":"Dataproc","icon":"images/dataproc_logo.svg","when":"config.cloudcode.beta.enableBigqueryExplorer","visibility":"collapsed"},{"id":"cloudcode.unified.notebookExplorer","name":"Notebooks","icon":"images/notebook_template_icon.svg","when":"config.cloudcode.beta.enableBigqueryExplorer","visibility":"collapsed"},{"id":"cloudcode.unified.bigQueryDatasetExplorer","name":"BigQuery Datasets","icon":"images/google_cloud.svg","when":"config.cloudcode.beta.enableBigqueryExplorer","visibility":"collapsed"},{"id":"cloudcode.unified.sec